{"tid":2205922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者：明日大嶼恐耗盡儲備 損聯滙","createTime":"2020-09-17T06:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T07:11:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cac2316836ea97dacdeeed9f69c4faaf0203c65","tid":2205922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:53:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/GUH753RAXZH37I4T5IPFMHWZMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FGUH753RAXZH37I4T5IPFMHWZMI%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=137a335e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FGUH753RAXZH37I4T5IPFMHWZMI%2F&h=8e3fad88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/GUH753RAXZH37I4T5IPFMHWZMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學者：明日大嶼恐耗盡儲備 損聯滙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n6Bh0x_uH9saelJVatWu3AGckzE=/720x584/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KV7FFDVZ4JBBDIGTJJYLO44PLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn6Bh0x_uH9saelJVatWu3AGckzE%3D%2F720x584%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKV7FFDVZ4JBBDIGTJJYLO44PLQ.jpg&h=0aa2b540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府本年度財赤料擴至3,000億元，但仍死心不息力推明日大嶼填海計劃。有環保團體與商業及經濟研究中心研究發現，若政府硬推明日大嶼，11年內勢耗盡財政儲備。有建制派議員建議政府發債籌集資金，但專家批評政府發債等於自行暴露財政實力不足，在維繫聯繫滙率方面出現信心危機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘發債或遭評級公司狙擊<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平聯同冠域商業及經濟研究中心近日發表《明日大嶼對香港財政的影響分析》報告。負責報告的該研究中心主任關焯照（圖）昨在港台節目明言，明日大嶼「條數計出嚟好唔掂」，由前財政司司長曾俊華在任時曾進行長遠財政計劃工作小組報告，指香港人口老化，最快2021至2022年會進入結構性財赤，即政府支出不斷高於收入，結果耗盡儲備，令公共財政可持續性受嚴重衝擊，香港或會被評級公司下降評級。<br />\n<br />\n他指明日大嶼人工島預計2025年至2026年始興建，但據現時估算政府2031年將用光儲備，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平資深項目主任連佩怡在同一節目指，東大嶼和鄰近水域有獨特生態價值，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯盧偉國指，最重要是推出工務工程讓業界「有工開」，明日大嶼、。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，關焯照批評政府發債等於自行暴露財政實力不足，令香港被評級公司攻擊，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n發展局回覆指，政府建議研究在交椅洲附近發展人工島，是考慮到該方案對香港未來所帶來龐大公眾裨益，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"4932201034956086c13a0c6aefd6700568159702","tid":2205922,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"大罪為名送錢為實？"},{"pid":"f54ad6c58c3b73aa4639e412c0c08ceb58c10a3a","tid":2205922,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"洗哂佢囉 好開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4416e3d3807138cae58fce17b3b1a606c8146338","tid":2205922,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:08:25.000Z","msg":"非常支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先破後立"},{"pid":"bf6381eb8e4967fb3508d035f67994077f659645","tid":2205922,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"快啲駛晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded240b706852406e756c5c7c27f9d4c612392ec","tid":2205922,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"加速主義好"},{"pid":"04830b91a0ef8ed085b6c2d9bbb95aacf44136e5","tid":2205922,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"明眼睇好明顯係香港死之前拎走哂d錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}